#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.accuracy_score.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.accuracy\\_score"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:1 of
msgid "Accuracy classification score."
msgstr "准确率分类评分。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:3 of
msgid ""
"In multilabel classification, this function computes subset accuracy: the"
" set of labels predicted for a sample must *exactly* match the "
"corresponding set of labels in y_true."
msgstr ""
"在多标签分类中，此函数计算子集准确率：样本预测的标签集必须与 y_true 中"
"对应的标签集*完全*匹配。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:7 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <accuracy_score>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <accuracy_score>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:9 of
msgid "Ground truth (correct) labels."
msgstr "真实（正确）标签。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:11 of
msgid "Predicted labels, as returned by a classifier."
msgstr "由分类器返回的预测标签。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:13 of
msgid ""
"If ``False``, return the number of correctly classified samples. "
"Otherwise, return the fraction of correctly classified samples."
msgstr "如果为 ``False``，则返回正确分类的样本数。否则，返回正确分类样本的比例。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:16 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:19 of
msgid ""
"**score** -- If ``normalize == True``, return the fraction of correctly "
"classified samples (float), else returns the number of correctly "
"classified samples (int).  The best performance is 1 with ``normalize == "
"True`` and the number of samples with ``normalize == False``."
msgstr ""
"**score** -- 如果 ``normalize == True``，则返回正确分类样本的比例（float"
"），否则返回正确分类样本的数量（int）。最佳性能是当 ``normalize == True``"
" 时为 1，当 ``normalize == False`` 时为样本数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:19 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**score** -- If ``normalize == True``, return the fraction of correctly "
"classified samples (float), else returns the number of correctly "
"classified samples (int)."
msgstr ""
"**score** -- 如果 ``normalize == True``，则返回正确分类样本的比例（float"
"），否则返回正确分类样本的数量（int）。最佳性能是当 ``normalize == True``"
" 时为 1，当 ``normalize == False`` 时为样本数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.accuracy_score:23 of
msgid ""
"The best performance is 1 with ``normalize == True`` and the number of "
"samples with ``normalize == False``."
msgstr ""

